rComments: She is probably one of the best professors I have ever had. She really knows her stuff which makes her lectures very interesting. Readings were long but fairly easy to get through. She goes through it in class in depth, so there is not too much to worry if you don't get it. I would 100% take her course again

Best professor and best class ever. She really cares about every student in her class. The readings are not very easy but she explains every concept very very clearly. The test is quite easy if you attend class and take good notes.

One of the best professor on campus! Material might not be the easiest but Laura is always willing to help! Her lectures are very informative as she summarize all the important details. If you take notes you will do fine. She is also very specific and does you exactly what is going to be on the exam so you can prepare for it! Highly recommended!

Absolutely love this prof. She is amazing. Learnt so much and she actually connects to all the students! She obviously loves what she does and I would take this class again in a heartbeat. Super approachable and nice and wants you to get a good mark! Best class of my 4 yrs.
